Name: Automaton Direwolf
Desc: An automaton pieced together with Old World technology. This rare type of humanoid automaton is equipped with a chainsaw on its right arm, presumably used for mining or construction operations.\nIn combat, Automaton Direwolfs will use their chainsaw to Bleed enemies, dealing DoT.

SkillList.SkillDesc: Deals massive Physical DMG to a single target, with a chance to Bleed the hit target. If the hit target is not Shielded, then a random ally of theirs suffers "Dismantle" for 1 time.
Locks Onto a single target. The next action on the target will cast "Felling Order."
Deals minor Physical DMG to a single target, with a high chance to inflict 1 stack of Bleed.
